      "timestamp": "2026-03-19T14:40:44+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "jonah-goldberg",
      "voiceName": "Jonah Goldberg",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "I think it\u2019s darkly funny that Hegseth thinks it\u2019s reassuring to hear him petulantly attack the media and insist it\u2019s just not true that we are spiraling into an \u201cendless abyss.\u201d",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/JonahDispatch/status/2034603173596340272",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-19T12:09:32+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
